{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01PnaRG6ozKhfxviUtabT2Ct","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The certificate rotation is complete. Here's a summary of what was done:\n\n**Before:** Server cert expired Jun 26 2026 (2-day remaining validity).\n\n**Steps taken:**\n1. Extracted the CA cert and key from the `mongodb-tls-ca` secret into the `openssl-toolbox` pod.\n2. Generated a new 2048-bit RSA server key and CSR with the same CN (`mongo-rs`) and all original SANs (localhost, mongo, mongo.mongodb.svc.cluster.local, and all 3 pod-specific DNS names).\n3. Signed the CSR with the existing CA for 365 days — CA trust is unchanged.\n4. Concatenated cert+key into `server.pem` and patched the `mongodb-tls-cert` secret.\n5. Performed a rolling restart of the `mongo-rs` StatefulSet — pods restarted one at a time, keeping the replica set available throughout.\n\n**After:** All 3 pods are Running, TLS handshake verifies OK (return code 0), and the live cert is valid **Jun 24 2026 → Jun 24 2027**."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":246,"cache_read_input_tokens":49727,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":246},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"f54fa9d6-87ac-4510-ae5f-d86c0b2fb857","uuid":"22e9081f-43fd-4755-bd73-2f9600feb7f1","request_id":"req_011CcMXLsric66ZR7hHv3URh"}
